node.text:
Can’t quite describe how surreal it felt to be on stage again after such a long break. 
I felt like there was so much appreciation and happiness in the room…
Can’t wait for the world to fully return to normal!! 

🎥: @chrisyoder

node.title: my first show in over 15 months

node.text:
some of you may recognize the beginning. Started writing this piece years ago and turned it into my intro for a while. Just now finished writing the second half... now it’s time to start producing it. :)
I’m wrote this wanting to be EDM but strongly influenced by classical music. 
When the song comes out u can go back to this video and see how it started :). PS: true colors came out 5 years ago so HAPPY BDAY TRUE COLORS 🤍

node.text:
Since I was 4 years old I have been writing music. My biggest dream was to one day not have to do anything other than music in my life. 
One decade ago I decided to add one more project to my music portfolio. After making classical music, Jazz, rock, metal, I started an electronic music project, ZEDD.
One decade later I am living the dream I always had. I make music. All day, every day. 
For that, I wanna thank you all so very much. The things I have achieved and was allowed to experience would never be possible without all the support and love from YOU. 
I’m lucky to work with the best team anyone could wish for, and have the most supportive fans.
It’s incredibly easy for me to be able to say that this decade was obviously the best decade of my life.
So today is the perfect day to just say:
Thank you 🤍

node.text: Hey guys, I'm super excited to officially kick off the #goodthingchallenge. The #goodthingchallenge is all about doing something good for somebody else. Whether it's donating to a charity, buying a coffee for the person in line behind you, or just doing something kind to brighten up somebody's day, I want to challenge all of you to do a good thing. Please share your moment with me on socials and use #goodthingchallenge & tag me so I can see it and repost! :) To kick off the challenge, I donated 10k USD to a Pediatric Cancer Research Foundation, and I want to nominate three of my friends @ninja, @jaredleto, and @daviddobrik, and uuuu to go out there and do a good thing too!!! ♥️
